LINK 800
LINK 799

REPL AZIMUTH
REPL ELEVATION
JUMP FREQUENCY

MARK AZIMUTH
LINK 800
SUBI #AZIM M X
JUMP ALIGN

MARK ELEVATION
LINK 801
SUBI #ELEV M X
JUMP ALIGN

MARK FREQUENCY
NOOP
NOOP
NOOP
COPY M #FREQ
HALT

MARK ALIGN
TEST X > 0
TJMP ALIGN_LOWER
TEST X < 0
TJMP ALIGN_HIGHER
HALT

MARK ALIGN_LOWER
COPY -1 #MOTR
SUBI X 1 X
TEST X > 0
TJMP ALIGN_LOWER
HALT

MARK ALIGN_HIGHER
COPY 1 #MOTR
ADDI X 1 X
TEST X < 0
TJMP ALIGN_HIGHER